headline: 3 Top High-Yield Dividend Stocks I Plan to Buy in March for More Passive Income
summary: Generating passive income is a core aspect of my financial strategy.  My goal is to eventually produce enough recurring investment income to cover my basic living expenses.  This March, I plan to buy several, including PepsiCo (NASDAQ: PEP), Johnson & Johnson (NYSE: JNJ), and Prologis (NYSE: PLD).
